msgid "# Thug _Medium humanoid (any race), any non-good alignment_"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/thug.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Armor Class** 11 (leather armor)    \n"
"**Hit Points** 32 (5d8 + 10)    \n"
"**Speed** 30 ft. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/thug.md:15
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"| STR     | DEX     | CON     | INT     | WIS     | CHA     |\n"
"|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|\n"
"| 15 (+2) | 11 (+0) | 14 (+2) | 10 (+0) | 10 (+0) | 11 (+0) |   \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/thug.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Skills** Intimidation +2    \n"
"**Senses** passive Perception 10    \n"
"**Languages** any one language (usually Common)    \n"
"**Challenge** 1/2 (100 XP) \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/thug.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Pack Tactics.** The thug has advantage on an attack roll against a "
"creature if at least one of the thug's allies is within 5 feet of the "
"creature and the ally isn't incapacitated. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/thug.md:27
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"### Actions \n"
"**Multiattack.** The thug makes two melee attacks.    \n"
"**Mace.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one "
"creature. _Hit:_ 5 (1d6 + 2) bludgeoning damage.    \n"
"**Heavy Crossbow.** _Ranged Weapon Attack:_ +2 to hit, range 100/400 ft., "
"one target. _Hit:_ 5 (1d10) piercing damage. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/thug.md:29
msgid ""
"### Description Thugs are ruthless enforcers skilled at intimidation and "
"violence. They work for money and have few scruples."
msgstr ""
